channel.title: [Apollo] Looking for experienced programmer(s)
channel.description:
Hello, i'm going to start a new project soon and i don't really have a lot of free time to work on the server. If you would like to join you must know how to work with [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,526031.msg3830874.html]Apollo[/url] and show me some of your work.
My project will be a server with Economy,Quests,Minigames,and Skills but mainly Pking. I currently have: Firemaking,Cooking,Woodcutting, basic combat(ranged,melee&magic).
I will read this thread Tomorrow maybe i don't have much time now i just leave this apply form here :)
[code] Your name: How old are you?: E-mail address/skype?: How long have you coded?: What time zone are you in?: How long will you be on everyday?: Why do you want to become part of this server?: Link to some of your work: Any Suggestions?:[/code]
Edit: Looking for a website developer!
